snippet.title: Octopath Traveler - Overview Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Eight travelers. Eight adventures. Eight roles to play in a new world brought to life by Square Enix. Choose the path you wish to walk and discover what lies beyond the horizon. Available now, only on Nintendo Switch.

Learn more about Octopath Traveler! https://octopathtraveler.nintendo.com

#NintendoSwitch #OctopathTraveler
